dc_description_s: This data layer represents building footprints in Dane County, Wisconsin in 2010. [This dataset contains building polygon data for Dane County. The dataset consists of structures the size of a single car garage or larger for Dane County, WI excluding structures within the City of Madison. In the City of Madison, building polygons are included for structures the size of a duplex or larger, except for around the Isthmus area.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/.
